# Game Controller to ETC EOS Interface

## Summary

An application to connect game pads with EOS, primarily for use when building or updating focus palettes.

### Supported functions
- Pan / Tilt
- Zoom, Iris, Edge
- Coarse / Fine Toggle
- Rem Dim, Next, Last, Select Last

## Usage

App will search for controllers and list them, if only one controller is found then it will be monitored and a connection opened to start sending to EOS on the local computer.
If you have more than 1 contoller, select from the list and tap Start Monitoring, then tap Connect.

### Requirements

ETC EOS Nomad

Enable OSC RX and UDP Port 8000

For setup detail refer to [ETC EOS User Guide - OSC](https://www.etcconnect.com/WebDocs/Controls/EosFamilyOnlineHelp/en/Content/23_Show_Control/08_OSC/OPEN_SOUND_CONTROL.htm?Highlight=OSC)


